            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>soy sauce</strong> with 150ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Drain and add your<strong> king prawns</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min or until the prawns are cooked through – this is your <strong>king</strong> <strong>prawn & sugar snap stir-fry</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
