          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the prawns are cooking, add your <strong>gochujang paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan with the rice with a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and mix until completely combined</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min further or until slightly crispy on the bottom – this is your <strong>gochujang fried rice</strong></p>",
