    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>gochujang fried rice</strong> with the <strong>king prawn & sugar snap stir-fry</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
